{"id":411335,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/10/立场新闻-彭丽媛访英化妆失败照-遭微博河蟹/","date":"2015-10-22T13:29:49Z","modified":"2015-10-22T18:01:05Z","title":"立场新闻 | 彭丽媛访英化妆失败照 遭微博河蟹","content":"<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/pang-09_jJ9o7_1200x0.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-411336\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/pang-09_jJ9o7_1200x0.png\" alt=\"彭丽媛化妆失败\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/pang-09_jJ9o7_1200x0.png 750w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/pang-09_jJ9o7_1200x0-300x200.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>中国国家主席习近平夫人彭丽媛，常被大陆媒体吹捧成时尚指标的地位，但在偕夫访英期间失手，被外国摄影记拍到脸上出现不均匀白粉，被戏称为「化妆失败」、「化妆事故」，外媒、港台媒体大肆报道，但在中国大陆网络，彭丽媛的这张照片则被「河蟹」；在新浪微博上，连发帖的网民帐号亦遭屏蔽。</p>\n<p>根据监测屏蔽微博的网站「<a href=\"https://freeweibo.com/weibo/3900666981957058\" target=\"_blank\">自由微博</a>」，上载彭丽媛「化妆事故」照片的微博，已经被删除，转发者微博亦被屏蔽。从<a href=\"http://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:4YZlGL-LKf8J:weibo.com/5718066597/D0hlM8d7s+&amp;cd=1&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;ct=clnk&amp;gl=hk#_rnd1445487298170\" target=\"_blank\">Google cache记录</a>亦可见，有关微博已无法访问，而发帖者的帐号目前已经失效。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_411337\" style=\"width: 610px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/7854756456456_xMEVU_1200x0.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-411337\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/7854756456456_xMEVU_1200x0.jpg\" alt=\"Google cache记录 该微博现无法访问\" width=\"600\" height=\"325\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/7854756456456_xMEVU_1200x0.jpg 617w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/7854756456456_xMEVU_1200x0-300x162.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Google cache记录 该微博现无法访问</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_411338\" style=\"width: 610px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/45456415145145_ZJ9eC_1200x0.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-411338\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/45456415145145_ZJ9eC_1200x0.jpg\" alt=\"发帖者微博目前「异常」\" width=\"600\" height=\"315\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/45456415145145_ZJ9eC_1200x0.jpg 982w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/45456415145145_ZJ9eC_1200x0-300x157.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">发帖者微博目前「异常」</p></div>\n<p>微博上亦有网民讨论有关微博被删除的事：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/75456456454156_RnX3J_1200x0.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-411339\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/75456456454156_RnX3J_1200x0.jpg\" alt=\"75456456454156_RnX3J_1200x0\" width=\"554\" height=\"529\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/75456456454156_RnX3J_1200x0.jpg 554w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/75456456454156_RnX3J_1200x0-300x286.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 554px) 100vw, 554px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/45764684564125_xmuVN_1200x0.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-411340\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/45764684564125_xmuVN_1200x0.jpg\" alt=\"45764684564125_xmuVN_1200x0\" width=\"600\" height=\"145\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/45764684564125_xmuVN_1200x0.jpg 704w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/45764684564125_xmuVN_1200x0-300x72.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>另一方面，英国《每日邮报》将彭丽媛形容为「前摇滚明星」（former rock star），亦激起网民联想（下图）。目前，此微博尚未被屏蔽，但网民纷纷在下方为专页点蜡烛及称「坐等贵博新号」。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen20Shot202015-10-2220at2012.25.1020PM_JxwoJ_1200x0.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-411341\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen20Shot202015-10-2220at2012.25.1020PM_JxwoJ_1200x0.png\" alt=\"Screen20Shot202015-10-2220at2012.25.1020PM_JxwoJ_1200x0\" width=\"597\" height=\"2016\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen20Shot202015-10-2220at2012.25.1020PM_JxwoJ_1200x0.png 597w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen20Shot202015-10-2220at2012.25.1020PM_JxwoJ_1200x0-89x300.png 89w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen20Shot202015-10-2220at2012.25.1020PM_JxwoJ_1200x0-303x1024.png 303w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 597px) 100vw, 597px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>*中国数字时代编辑注：</strong><br />\n澳大利亚小报《Herald Tabloid》还总结了<a href=\"http://www.heraldsun.com.au/entertainment/celebrity/chinas-first-lady-peng-liyuan-joins-list-of-celebrities-who-have-suffered-make-up-malfunctions/story-fni0bn7b-1227571851040?sv=4b94d61e4d5f0dec5169f210d679d2e2\">其他女明星与彭丽媛相似的妆容失败照</a>，并解释道，这种受女明星欢迎的化妆品是HD定妆粉。肉眼看和摄像机拍摄都不会显示出来，只有在照相机的闪光灯下可能会显现。</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,18424],"tags":[28861,28953,28954,18012,8620,28952]}